Notepad++ => Shortcuts:
----------------------

Editing Shortcuts:

cntl + X => cut
cntl + C => copy
cntl + V => paste

cntl + A => select all
cntl + Z => undo
cntl + Y => redo

cntl + F => find
cntl + H => replace
cntl + S => save
cntl + O => open

cntl + N => open new tab
cntl + W => close current tab

cntl + B => match brackets
cntl + G => goto

F11 => full screen
F12 => post-it mode [no tap/down tool bar]

tab => indent
shift + tab => remove indent

cntl + shift + up key => move current line up
cntl + shift + down key => move current line down

cntl + shift + U => to upper case
cntl + U => to lower case

cntl + D => duplicate current line
cntl + L => cut current line
cntl + shift + L => delete current line

cntl + T => switch current line with previous line
cntl + J => join lines

cntl + Q => toggle line comment
cntl + shift + Q => block comment

alt + mouse drag => column select
alt + C => column editor

alt + F4 => exit notepad

cntl + page up => previous tab
cntl + page down => next tab

cntl + backspace => delete to start of word
cntl + delete => delete to end of word

cntl + shift + backspace => delete to start of line
cntl + shift + delete => delete to end of line

cntl + alt + enter => create blank line above current line
cntl + alt + shift + enter => create blank line below current line

cntl + enter => word completion
cntl + space => function list

cntl + alt + R => right oriented text
cntl + alt + L => left oriented text [default]

cntl + shift + T => open recently closed tab



















